1
00:00:44,100 --> 00:00:48,700
=The Hidden Heir Ye Chen=
(Adapted from "The Peerless Son-in-Law")

2
00:00:49,420 --> 00:00:51,780
=Episode 8=

3
00:00:52,520 --> 00:00:53,719
This Jumping Carp

4
00:00:53,719 --> 00:00:56,520
is one of our signature dishes
at Weiding Pavilion.

5
00:00:56,799 --> 00:00:58,159
Hope you all enjoy your meal.

6
00:00:58,600 --> 00:00:59,359
Thank you.

7
00:01:01,880 --> 00:01:02,439
Ruolin,

8
00:01:03,039 --> 00:01:03,840
what's wrong?

9
00:01:04,200 --> 00:01:05,359
It's been two years.

10
00:01:05,560 --> 00:01:07,640
I didn't expect Xiao Hailong
to still be the same.

11
00:01:08,759 --> 00:01:09,960
But Ye Chen,

12
00:01:10,799 --> 00:01:11,920
you've changed a lot.

13
00:01:12,920 --> 00:01:13,680
Me?

14
00:01:15,200 --> 00:01:17,920
Wasn't I always this handsome?

15
00:01:19,280 --> 00:01:21,079
I meant you're more energetic now.

16
00:01:22,799 --> 00:01:24,120
Good things make people feel good.

17
00:01:24,640 --> 00:01:26,920
I've been riding
on Ms. Xiao's coattails lately.

18
00:01:28,239 --> 00:01:29,719
Why do I feel like

19
00:01:29,719 --> 00:01:31,280
I'm the one riding on your coattails?

20
00:01:32,959 --> 00:01:35,200
We're like a mutual support system.

21
00:01:35,680 --> 00:01:36,280
Let's eat.

22
00:01:36,640 --> 00:01:38,040
By the way, Ruolin,

23
00:01:38,519 --> 00:01:40,490
what made you decide
to come back here for work?

24
00:01:40,719 --> 00:01:41,680
As you know,

25
00:01:41,840 --> 00:01:43,680
big families have their own issues.

26
00:01:44,159 --> 00:01:45,959
I didn't want to get involved.

27
00:01:46,640 --> 00:01:48,079
I happened to read an interview

28
00:01:48,079 --> 00:01:50,680
with Wang Dongxue,
the chairperson of Dihao, in a magazine.

29
00:01:51,040 --> 00:01:52,239
I really like her.

30
00:01:52,250 --> 00:01:54,290
She's the perfect example
of an independent woman.

31
00:01:54,920 --> 00:01:55,799
I came back this time

32
00:01:56,439 --> 00:01:58,200
to join Dihao Group

33
00:01:58,519 --> 00:01:59,599
and learn from her.

34
00:02:00,280 --> 00:02:03,599
Coincidentally, Churan's been
working with Dihao recently.

35
00:02:04,519 --> 00:02:06,319
They're so close, like best friends.

36
00:02:06,319 --> 00:02:07,040
Really?

37
00:02:07,040 --> 00:02:07,439
Yeah.

38
00:02:07,599 --> 00:02:09,439
I've been trying
to figure out how to get in.

39
00:02:09,799 --> 00:02:10,439
Churan,

40
00:02:11,000 --> 00:02:12,280
help me out.

41
00:02:13,560 --> 00:02:14,800
Actually,

42
00:02:15,240 --> 00:02:16,719
you should ask Ye Chen.

43
00:02:17,280 --> 00:02:19,319
The reason I got this deal with Dihao

44
00:02:19,520 --> 00:02:21,000
is all thanks to him.

45
00:02:21,319 --> 00:02:22,159
Chen,

46
00:02:22,159 --> 00:02:23,159
please help me out.

47
00:02:23,879 --> 00:02:24,759
Don't say that.

48
00:02:25,159 --> 00:02:26,479
If Churan's in, I'm in.

49
00:02:27,199 --> 00:02:27,759
Churan...

50
00:02:27,759 --> 00:02:28,680
If Ye Chen's in,

51
00:02:28,840 --> 00:02:30,199
I'm in.

52
00:02:30,439 --> 00:02:31,520
Since everyone's in,

53
00:02:31,759 --> 00:02:32,680
there's no issue, right?

54
00:02:33,120 --> 00:02:33,719
Exactly.

55
00:02:35,919 --> 00:02:36,599
Cheers.

56
00:02:37,719 --> 00:02:39,360
I haven't hugged you in a while.

57
00:02:39,360 --> 00:02:40,400
You still smell so good.

58
00:02:41,439 --> 00:02:42,479
You pervert.

59
00:02:44,080 --> 00:02:45,520
I pushed Ye Chen out.

60
00:02:45,520 --> 00:02:46,639
Do you think he'll be mad?

61
00:02:47,159 --> 00:02:47,800
No.

62
00:02:48,159 --> 00:02:50,199
Just settle in here.

63
00:02:50,199 --> 00:02:51,599
- No need to rush to rent a place.
- Okay.

64
00:02:56,960 --> 00:02:57,520
Look.

65
00:02:57,520 --> 00:02:58,340
(Ye Chen: She can start tomorrow.)

66
00:02:59,360 --> 00:03:00,879
Thank you, Churan.

67
00:03:00,879 --> 00:03:02,220
Make sure to thank Ye Chen for me.

68
00:03:05,680 --> 00:03:06,159
Ruolin,

69
00:03:06,479 --> 00:03:08,400
you'll be working
with Ms. Jiang for now.

70
00:03:08,400 --> 00:03:09,199
Okay, got it.

71
00:03:09,360 --> 00:03:09,840
Good luck.

72
00:03:10,039 --> 00:03:11,759
Make sure to learn a lot here.

73
00:03:11,759 --> 00:03:12,159
I will.

74
00:03:13,560 --> 00:03:14,439
Thank you, Ms. Wang.

75
00:03:14,479 --> 00:03:14,879
Welcome.

76
00:03:14,879 --> 00:03:15,719
Thanks, Chen.

77
00:03:19,240 --> 00:03:21,240
Not bad. You're pretty reliable.

78
00:03:21,719 --> 00:03:23,479
Dongxue, thanks for the help.

79
00:03:24,120 --> 00:03:25,759
No need to be so polite with me.

80
00:03:35,500 --> 00:03:37,280
It's been so long
since I've gone shopping.

81
00:03:37,840 --> 00:03:39,199
I've been so busy lately.

82
00:03:39,960 --> 00:03:41,479
How's it going at Dihao lately?

83
00:03:41,479 --> 00:03:42,520
Are you getting used to it?

84
00:03:43,319 --> 00:03:43,840
It's great.

85
00:03:44,199 --> 00:03:45,919
Ms. Wang is really nice.

86
00:03:47,080 --> 00:03:49,039
Also, I haven't thanked you.

87
00:03:49,110 --> 00:03:50,759
I'll take you both
out for dinner sometime.

88
00:03:50,759 --> 00:03:52,479
Why are you being so polite with me?

89
00:03:52,479 --> 00:03:54,240
Let's talk after you've settled in.

90
00:03:56,319 --> 00:03:56,960
Churan,

91
00:03:57,439 --> 00:03:58,479
I have a gossip question.

92
00:03:59,599 --> 00:04:01,759
What's the relationship

93
00:04:01,759 --> 00:04:03,039
between Ye Chen and Ms. Wang?

94
00:04:04,479 --> 00:04:05,159
The two of them?

95
00:04:05,520 --> 00:04:07,199
They don't have
any special relationship.

96
00:04:08,439 --> 00:04:10,479
I'm just curious.

97
00:04:10,879 --> 00:04:11,919
Their relationship seems

98
00:04:12,400 --> 00:04:13,599
a bit more than just ordinary.

99
00:04:15,960 --> 00:04:17,080
Their relationship

100
00:04:17,479 --> 00:04:19,280
is pretty ordinary.

101
00:04:19,639 --> 00:04:20,919
Don't jump to conclusions.

102
00:04:20,919 --> 00:04:22,110
They don't have anything going on.

103
00:04:22,120 --> 00:04:23,240
I knew it.

104
00:04:23,800 --> 00:04:26,040
How could there be anything going on

105
00:04:26,040 --> 00:04:27,319
between Ms. Wang and Chen?

106
00:04:29,279 --> 00:04:30,560
But Churan,

107
00:04:30,560 --> 00:04:31,959
I have to tell you.

108
00:04:31,959 --> 00:04:33,399
You should keep a close eye on Chen.

109
00:04:34,160 --> 00:04:35,560
It's not that I don't trust him,

110
00:04:35,560 --> 00:04:36,360
but after all,

111
00:04:36,879 --> 00:04:37,800
he's a man.

112
00:04:44,399 --> 00:04:45,120
Dad,

113
00:04:45,439 --> 00:04:46,399
what are you doing?

114
00:04:47,160 --> 00:04:48,199
Isn't Ye Chen's home?

115
00:04:49,600 --> 00:04:50,800
Yeah.

116
00:04:51,000 --> 00:04:52,319
He went out after taking a call.

117
00:04:52,319 --> 00:04:53,279
The pot's burnt.

118
00:04:53,279 --> 00:04:54,079
Where'd he go?

119
00:04:54,199 --> 00:04:55,040
- No idea.
- Ye Chen,

120
00:04:55,160 --> 00:04:56,319
you shameless thing.

121
00:04:56,600 --> 00:04:57,480
I'm coming for you.

122
00:04:57,480 --> 00:04:58,879
What? It's just a burnt pot.

123
00:04:58,900 --> 00:04:59,519
Why so serious?

124
00:04:59,720 --> 00:05:00,319
Burnt pot?

125
00:05:00,720 --> 00:05:01,360
He's ruined.

126
00:05:01,360 --> 00:05:02,360
Look at this.

127
00:05:02,800 --> 00:05:03,900
(Ye Chen Caught in Late-Night Meeting)
Wang Dongxue from Dihao Group

128
00:05:03,900 --> 00:05:05,020
(with Wang Dongxue)
is keeping a man.

129
00:05:05,380 --> 00:05:07,000
The Xiao family sells Ye Chen for honor.

130
00:05:07,000 --> 00:05:09,040
The son-in-law sells his charm.

131
00:05:09,040 --> 00:05:12,319
What's the relationship
between Ye Chen and Ms. Wang?

132
00:05:12,319 --> 00:05:13,759
You should keep a close eye on Chen.

133
00:05:13,879 --> 00:05:15,879
After all, he's a man.

134
00:05:16,040 --> 00:05:18,279
We can't just believe gossip.

135
00:05:18,279 --> 00:05:19,319
Shut up.

136
00:05:19,319 --> 00:05:21,480
He left after taking a call
from Wang Dongxue.

137
00:05:21,920 --> 00:05:24,399
He said he was going to Shengxia Hotel's

138
00:05:24,399 --> 00:05:25,920
presidential suite to meet her.

139
00:05:26,480 --> 00:05:27,519
I'm so pissed.

140
00:05:28,199 --> 00:05:28,560
Let's go.

141
00:05:29,110 --> 00:05:30,000
What are you doing?

142
00:05:30,010 --> 00:05:30,959
Catch them red-handed.

143
00:05:31,079 --> 00:05:33,600
Can we at least figure this out first?

144
00:05:33,839 --> 00:05:34,279
No way.

145
00:05:34,530 --> 00:05:36,279
Even if the Queen herself
shows up today,

146
00:05:36,639 --> 00:05:37,480
no one

147
00:05:37,480 --> 00:05:38,439
can bully my daughter.

148
00:05:44,319 --> 00:05:44,879
Mom,

149
00:05:45,480 --> 00:05:46,439
what are you doing?

150
00:05:47,000 --> 00:05:47,920
Just trust me.

151
00:05:48,199 --> 00:05:48,879
She's here.

152
00:05:50,319 --> 00:05:52,120
Hello, did you look for the front desk?

153
00:05:52,120 --> 00:05:53,120
The room's leaking.

154
00:05:53,120 --> 00:05:53,680
Look.

155
00:05:53,680 --> 00:05:54,480
Open the door now.

156
00:05:55,319 --> 00:05:57,199
I'm telling you,
my son-in-law is in there.

157
00:05:57,199 --> 00:05:58,240
He's out of his mind.

158
00:05:58,240 --> 00:05:59,439
If he faints in the bathroom...

159
00:05:59,439 --> 00:05:59,920
- Mom
- No.

160
00:06:00,360 --> 00:06:02,000
If he dies in there,
are you responsible?

161
00:06:02,199 --> 00:06:03,040
Open the door now.

162
00:06:03,040 --> 00:06:03,480
Okay.

163
00:06:08,480 --> 00:06:08,879
Mom.

164
00:06:08,879 --> 00:06:09,319
Wang Dongxue!

165
00:06:09,319 --> 00:06:09,759
Stop it, Mom.

166
00:06:09,759 --> 00:06:11,040
How dare you seduce Ye Chen?

167
00:06:11,040 --> 00:06:12,480
Sorry, Ms. Wang.

168
00:06:12,759 --> 00:06:13,399
What?

169
00:06:13,560 --> 00:06:14,519
Don't be so respectful.

170
00:06:14,520 --> 00:06:15,639
She's stealing your husband.

171
00:06:15,879 --> 00:06:16,759
You seductress.

172
00:06:16,759 --> 00:06:17,560
What are you doing?

173
00:06:17,560 --> 00:06:18,399
Where's Ye Chen?

174
00:06:18,399 --> 00:06:19,560
He's not here.

175
00:06:19,560 --> 00:06:20,290
You won't say, huh?

176
00:06:20,319 --> 00:06:21,800
I'll take a picture of you.

177
00:06:21,800 --> 00:06:23,560
