that will make you go viral.

178
00:06:23,560 --> 00:06:24,399
- Mom.
- Ye Chen.

179
00:06:24,600 --> 00:06:25,240
Stop it, Mom.

180
00:06:25,240 --> 00:06:25,879
Come out.

181
00:06:26,000 --> 00:06:27,199
You piece of trash.

182
00:06:27,199 --> 00:06:28,399
You think you're all that?

183
00:06:28,820 --> 00:06:29,959
How dare you betray Churan?

184
00:06:29,959 --> 00:06:30,600
Calm down.

185
00:06:30,600 --> 00:06:31,160
Stop it.

186
00:06:31,160 --> 00:06:31,839
Ye Chen, come out.

187
00:06:31,839 --> 00:06:33,040
You two cheating lovers.

188
00:06:33,050 --> 00:06:34,120
- Where's Ye Chen?
- Mom.

189
00:06:34,120 --> 00:06:35,000
I told you already.

190
00:06:35,000 --> 00:06:36,040
He's not here.

191
00:06:36,279 --> 00:06:37,560
Just because you say so?

192
00:06:37,720 --> 00:06:38,639
I don't believe you.

193
00:06:38,839 --> 00:06:39,680
Get out of the way.

194
00:06:39,680 --> 00:06:40,279
Ms. Wang.

195
00:06:43,439 --> 00:06:44,040
Mom.

196
00:06:44,839 --> 00:06:45,720
Very well.

197
00:06:46,360 --> 00:06:48,279
You're done?

198
00:06:49,399 --> 00:06:51,040
And you're telling me he's not here?

199
00:06:54,000 --> 00:06:55,319
I've got you this time.

200
00:06:56,639 --> 00:06:57,720
Get out of the way.

201
00:06:57,839 --> 00:06:58,199
Ms. Wang.

202
00:06:58,199 --> 00:07:00,199
Ye Chen, you jerk.

203
00:07:00,199 --> 00:07:01,000
I'll beat you up.

204
00:07:01,600 --> 00:07:02,720
I'll definitely beat you up.

205
00:07:03,279 --> 00:07:04,279
You loser.

206
00:07:04,300 --> 00:07:05,480
- I'll beat you up.
- Stop it.

207
00:07:05,480 --> 00:07:05,920
I'll beat you up.

208
00:07:05,920 --> 00:07:06,639
Please stop.

209
00:07:06,639 --> 00:07:07,199
Stop it.

210
00:07:07,199 --> 00:07:08,519
Stop it. It's me, Mrs. Xiao.

211
00:07:08,519 --> 00:07:09,639
Mrs. Xiao, it's me.

212
00:07:09,639 --> 00:07:10,639
It's me, Wang Daokun.

213
00:07:10,800 --> 00:07:11,639
Wang Daokun.

214
00:07:11,639 --> 00:07:12,800
Yes, I'm beating you up.

215
00:07:15,639 --> 00:07:17,079
I'm Wang Daokun.

216
00:07:17,639 --> 00:07:18,920
Wang Daokun?

217
00:07:23,180 --> 00:07:25,620
(Wang Daokun, Ye Chen's college friend)

218
00:07:26,759 --> 00:07:27,720
Ms. Wang,

219
00:07:28,279 --> 00:07:30,079
I really didn't expect this.

220
00:07:30,759 --> 00:07:32,000
How did you end up...

221
00:07:32,439 --> 00:07:32,800
Yeah.

222
00:07:33,079 --> 00:07:34,040
I'm dating him.

223
00:07:34,720 --> 00:07:35,319
Right?

224
00:07:43,079 --> 00:07:45,879
Actually, I heard you
talking to Ye Chen on the phone,

225
00:07:46,040 --> 00:07:47,079
asking him to come here.

226
00:07:47,959 --> 00:07:48,560
Yeah.

227
00:07:48,759 --> 00:07:49,639
I did ask him to come.

228
00:07:54,360 --> 00:07:54,839
Churan, Mom?

229
00:07:54,839 --> 00:07:55,720
Why are you here?

230
00:08:00,079 --> 00:08:01,519
There are three of you?

231
00:08:01,759 --> 00:08:02,519
What?

232
00:08:03,600 --> 00:08:04,759
How did it get this messy?

233
00:08:04,759 --> 00:08:06,040
Mom, it's not what you think.

234
00:08:06,040 --> 00:08:06,970
- It's not.
- Enough.

235
00:08:07,360 --> 00:08:07,759
Kun,

236
00:08:08,120 --> 00:08:09,399
you take Ye Chen downstairs.

237
00:08:09,399 --> 00:08:10,360
I'll talk to them.

238
00:08:13,079 --> 00:08:14,279
It's really not what you think.

239
00:08:16,000 --> 00:08:16,990
- It's not...
- Come on.

240
00:08:17,240 --> 00:08:18,000
Your snacks...

241
00:08:21,260 --> 00:08:22,040
Please have a seat.

242
00:08:24,199 --> 00:08:26,160
Since you've already caught us,

243
00:08:26,480 --> 00:08:27,839
I've got nothing left to hide.

244
00:08:28,439 --> 00:08:29,720
Daokun and I...

245
00:08:30,079 --> 00:08:31,000
Daokun's a good guy.

246
00:08:32,040 --> 00:08:32,519
He's

247
00:08:33,000 --> 00:08:33,439
