249
00:08:35,360 --> 00:08:35,920
Hardworking.

250
00:08:36,279 --> 00:08:36,879
Down to earth.

251
00:08:38,360 --> 00:08:39,000
Ambitious.

252
00:08:39,000 --> 00:08:39,919
Alright.

253
00:08:40,759 --> 00:08:42,440
You don't have to force it.

254
00:08:46,500 --> 00:08:48,120
What are you going to do
with this money?

255
00:08:49,720 --> 00:08:51,240
Haven't decided yet.

256
00:08:51,960 --> 00:08:53,279
50 thousand yuan.

257
00:08:53,279 --> 00:08:55,240
Having a sugar mama is amazing.

258
00:08:56,120 --> 00:08:57,879
So you're just in it for the money?

259
00:08:57,879 --> 00:08:58,559
Duh?

260
00:08:58,559 --> 00:08:59,690
You think it's for you?

261
00:09:00,360 --> 00:09:01,440
Besides,

262
00:09:01,919 --> 00:09:04,519
I did make some effort.

263
00:09:04,519 --> 00:09:06,240
You really have no shame.

264
00:09:07,080 --> 00:09:08,320
So, I don't want

265
00:09:08,320 --> 00:09:10,159
the outside world to know
about me and Daokun.

266
00:09:10,679 --> 00:09:13,120
Of course,
Ye Chen also found out by accident.

267
00:09:13,120 --> 00:09:15,039
So he's been
helping us keep it a secret.

268
00:09:15,360 --> 00:09:17,559
Sometimes, he even helps cover for us.

269
00:09:19,720 --> 00:09:20,480
So,

270
00:09:20,799 --> 00:09:21,679
you and Ye Chen

271
00:09:21,879 --> 00:09:22,720
aren't...

272
00:09:24,399 --> 00:09:25,039
Right?

273
00:09:30,039 --> 00:09:31,360
I knew it.

274
00:09:31,360 --> 00:09:31,960
Ms. Wang.

275
00:09:34,919 --> 00:09:35,960
So,

276
00:09:36,919 --> 00:09:38,200
you were being so nice to me

277
00:09:38,639 --> 00:09:39,960
