278
00:09:41,879 --> 00:09:42,960
Well, that's part of it.

279
00:09:43,519 --> 00:09:45,360
And, of course,
Mr. Tang's part of it too.

280
00:09:47,039 --> 00:09:48,519
But the most important thing

281
00:09:49,320 --> 00:09:50,720
is that I believe in you.

282
00:09:52,080 --> 00:09:53,559
You're right about that.

283
00:09:53,559 --> 00:09:54,320
She's so great.

284
00:09:54,320 --> 00:09:55,159
She's awesome.

285
00:09:55,159 --> 00:09:57,039
She's been a top student
since she was little.

286
00:09:57,040 --> 00:09:58,200
You really have great taste.

287
00:09:58,200 --> 00:09:59,200
Mom, enough.

288
00:10:01,679 --> 00:10:02,600
Churan,

289
00:10:03,440 --> 00:10:04,480
those news reports online

290
00:10:04,679 --> 00:10:05,960
are just rumors.

291
00:10:06,440 --> 00:10:07,159
I'm sorry.

292
00:10:07,320 --> 00:10:08,080
No.

293
00:10:08,679 --> 00:10:10,279
It's our fault.

294
00:10:10,559 --> 00:10:12,039
This is your personal business.

295
00:10:12,600 --> 00:10:14,039
We were out of line.

296
00:10:14,039 --> 00:10:14,720
I'm sorry.

297
00:10:15,159 --> 00:10:15,799
No.

298
00:10:16,200 --> 00:10:16,799
It's me.

299
00:10:17,300 --> 00:10:18,080
It's all my fault.

300
00:10:18,559 --> 00:10:19,600
I'm just too impatient.

301
00:10:20,000 --> 00:10:21,440
Please don't hold it against me.

302
00:10:21,840 --> 00:10:22,600
Sorry.

303
00:10:23,240 --> 00:10:23,799
I'm sorry.

304
00:10:23,799 --> 00:10:24,399
Alright.

305
00:10:24,840 --> 00:10:26,399
Now that everything's cleared up,

306
00:10:27,080 --> 00:10:28,559
let's just leave this matter

307
00:10:28,559 --> 00:10:30,759
in this room.

308
00:10:30,759 --> 00:10:31,200
Okay?

309
00:10:31,399 --> 00:10:32,399
Don't worry.

310
00:10:32,720 --> 00:10:33,799
I won't say a word.

311
00:10:37,879 --> 00:10:38,639
Misunderstanding.

312
00:10:38,960 --> 00:10:40,120
It's a misunderstanding.

313
00:10:40,799 --> 00:10:41,840
We've cleared it up.

314
00:10:41,960 --> 00:10:43,039
Everything's clear.

315
00:10:43,399 --> 00:10:45,480
Ms. Wang is really forgiving.

316
00:10:45,480 --> 00:10:47,519
Mom, Churan, how about I take you home?

317
00:10:48,919 --> 00:10:50,159
Goodbye, Ms. Wang.

318
00:10:53,039 --> 00:10:54,279
I'll head out too.

319
00:10:54,279 --> 00:10:54,759
Okay.

320
00:10:55,200 --> 00:10:56,970
Come over to my place
to hang out sometime.

321
00:10:57,320 --> 00:10:57,720
Alright.

322
00:11:04,159 --> 00:11:05,399
Thanks, Daokun.

323
00:11:08,480 --> 00:11:09,120
No problem.

324
00:11:09,300 --> 00:11:10,990
Next time you need anything,
just call me.

325
00:11:11,100 --> 00:11:12,240
I'm at your beck and call.

326
00:11:16,600 --> 00:11:17,159
Ye Chen,

327
00:11:17,480 --> 00:11:18,159
listen up.

328
00:11:18,639 --> 00:11:19,960
Even though today's incident

329
00:11:20,159 --> 00:11:21,200
was a misunderstanding,

330
00:11:21,480 --> 00:11:22,759
there's no smoke without fire.

331
00:11:23,080 --> 00:11:23,600
You're right.

332
00:11:24,039 --> 00:11:24,720
From now on,

333
00:11:24,879 --> 00:11:26,759
you need to remember
to keep yourself pure.

334
00:11:27,050 --> 00:11:27,879
- Also...
- Noted.

335
00:11:31,159 --> 00:11:31,720
Hello?

336
00:11:33,000 --> 00:11:33,679
Mahjong?

337
00:11:34,320 --> 00:11:34,840
Wait for me.

338
00:11:34,919 --> 00:11:35,480
I'm coming.

339
00:11:38,039 --> 00:11:38,860
I'm meeting someone.

340
00:11:38,879 --> 00:11:40,159
You two go home by yourselves.

341
00:11:44,759 --> 00:11:45,559
Take care, Mom.

342
00:11:47,600 --> 00:11:48,320
Ye Chen,

343
00:11:48,679 --> 00:11:49,600
remember this.

344
00:11:49,799 --> 00:11:51,240
Keep yourself pure.

345
00:11:52,440 --> 00:11:53,159
Got it.

346
00:11:56,039 --> 00:11:56,919
Your bags.

347
00:12:04,000 --> 00:12:04,840
Take care, Mom.

348
00:12:05,480 --> 00:12:06,440
You're right.

349
00:12:06,919 --> 00:12:07,840
You've got a point.

350
00:12:08,720 --> 00:12:09,639
Keep myself pure.

351
00:12:10,240 --> 00:12:11,120
No smoke without fire.

352
00:12:12,000 --> 00:12:12,990
- Drop the act.
- It's all...

353
00:12:15,080 --> 00:12:16,039
I'm not acting.

354
00:12:16,600 --> 00:12:19,240
I really think Mom's got a point.

355
00:12:22,200 --> 00:12:22,960
But

356
00:12:22,960 --> 00:12:24,960
I know I made some mistakes first.

357
00:12:25,679 --> 00:12:28,000
The tricks you played might fool Mom,

358
00:12:28,500 --> 00:12:29,759
but you think they'll fool me?

359
00:12:30,360 --> 00:12:31,440
You think I'm that dumb?

360
00:12:31,679 --> 00:12:32,759
Wang Daokun

361
00:12:33,480 --> 00:12:35,000
and Ms. Wang?

362
00:12:35,000 --> 00:12:36,520
I can't believe you came up with that.

363
00:12:37,639 --> 00:12:39,679
The rumors spread too quickly.

364
00:12:39,679 --> 00:12:40,240
The...

365
00:12:40,240 --> 00:12:41,519
The script's not even ready yet.

366
00:12:42,440 --> 00:12:43,120
But I swear,

367
00:12:43,440 --> 00:12:45,560
Ms. Wang and I aren't
in that kind of relationship.

368
00:12:47,480 --> 00:12:49,799
I believe you two
don't have that kind of relationship.

369
00:12:52,759 --> 00:12:55,279
So what's going on
between you two, then?

370
00:12:58,080 --> 00:12:58,799
Well...

371
00:12:58,799 --> 00:12:59,360
Ye Chen,

372
00:12:59,879 --> 00:13:01,840
if you don't explain this to me today,

373
00:13:02,350 --> 00:13:03,840
I'll just quit being the chairperson.

374
00:13:04,639 --> 00:13:05,679
Don't.

375
00:13:06,759 --> 00:13:09,279
If you do that, then you've fallen
into the rumor makers' trap.

376
00:13:09,639 --> 00:13:10,360
Think about it.

377
00:13:10,720 --> 00:13:11,759
This rumor

378
00:13:11,759 --> 00:13:13,000
didn't come out of nowhere.

379
00:13:13,180 --> 00:13:14,279
There's a purpose behind it.

380
00:13:14,440 --> 00:13:15,360
It's to stop you

381
00:13:15,360 --> 00:13:16,720
from becoming chairperson.

382
00:13:17,679 --> 00:13:18,679
Really?

383
00:13:19,300 --> 00:13:21,440
Ms. Wang and Wang Daokun
are already investigating.

384
00:13:22,039 --> 00:13:23,159
Once the truth comes out...

385
00:13:23,519 --> 00:13:24,600
See? They're calling.

386
00:13:25,919 --> 00:13:26,559
It's really her.

387
00:13:26,559 --> 00:13:27,700
(Wang Dongxue)

388
00:13:28,919 --> 00:13:29,240
Hello?

389
00:13:29,500 --> 00:13:30,679
We found out who did this.

390
00:13:30,800 --> 00:13:31,240
Who is it?

391
00:13:31,639 --> 00:13:32,159
Dong Ruolin.

392
00:13:35,180 --> 00:13:36,420
(Ye Chen Caught in Late-Night Meeting
with Wang Dongxue)

393
00:13:38,159 --> 00:13:40,080
You didn't come back for a job.

394
00:13:41,200 --> 00:13:42,870
You're not here for Wang Dongxue either.

395
00:13:43,559 --> 00:13:45,000
You're just here to stir up trouble.

396
00:13:45,279 --> 00:13:46,200
Why?

397
00:13:49,159 --> 00:13:49,919
Ruolin,

398
00:13:51,720 --> 00:13:52,480
all these years,

399
00:13:52,480 --> 00:13:54,360
I've always thought of you
as my best friend.

400
00:13:55,120 --> 00:13:56,639
I know you're not that kind of person.

401
00:13:56,639 --> 00:13:58,039
You don't have bad intentions.

402
00:13:58,440 --> 00:13:59,759
Can you tell me

403
00:14:00,360 --> 00:14:01,840
why you're doing this?

404
00:14:03,320 --> 00:14:04,120
You should know

405
00:14:04,130 --> 00:14:05,960
Wang Dongxue is not someone
you can mess with.

406
00:14:06,279 --> 00:14:07,840
Dihao's legal team is no joke too.

407
00:14:08,679 --> 00:14:10,559
Do you really want them to sue you?

408
00:14:13,639 --> 00:14:14,320
I...

409
00:14:15,879 --> 00:14:17,159
I had no choice.

410
00:14:18,480 --> 00:14:20,120
My family's business is failing.

411
00:14:21,000 --> 00:14:22,559
We're almost bankrupt.

412
00:14:23,720 --> 00:14:25,840
Someone came to me

413
00:14:27,080 --> 00:14:28,990
and said they could
save our family with money.

414
00:14:30,639 --> 00:14:31,360
I had...

415
00:14:31,879 --> 00:14:33,360
I had no choice but to accept.

416
00:14:34,519 --> 00:14:35,559
Who is this person?

417
00:14:37,960 --> 00:14:39,120
You knew all along.

418
00:14:39,759 --> 00:14:41,960
You purposely set me up as a target?

419
00:14:42,240 --> 00:14:43,960
Bring me the medicine formula,

420
00:14:44,350 --> 00:14:45,639
and I'll make sure you're safe.

421
00:15:07,262 --> 00:15:09,750
♪They said I was only meant
to gaze at the light♪

422
00:15:09,837 --> 00:15:13,590
♪Never knowing I am the flame itself♪

423
00:15:14,050 --> 00:15:18,987
♪I am fireworks, not a fire cast aside♪

424
00:15:19,150 --> 00:15:21,437
♪I open my eyes amid the ruins♪

425
00:15:21,750 --> 00:15:24,430
♪No one shields me
from the wind or the sky♪

426
00:15:25,500 --> 00:15:28,125
♪Let them mock, let them sneer♪

427
00:15:28,425 --> 00:15:31,437
♪I sharpen my silence into blades♪

428
00:15:31,637 --> 00:15:34,687
♪Every cold word, I remember♪

429
00:15:34,800 --> 00:15:37,762
♪Etching my path of defiance
into my heart♪

430
00:15:38,030 --> 00:15:41,187
♪Fate did not sign my future for me♪

431
00:15:41,412 --> 00:15:45,162
♪I carved my own light
with clenched fists♪

432
00:15:45,162 --> 00:15:48,025
♪I belong to no one♪

433
00:15:48,087 --> 00:15:51,537
♪I am the ember
that refuses to bow to destiny♪

434
00:15:51,537 --> 00:15:54,212
♪Even if the world burns me into ash♪

435
00:15:54,212 --> 00:16:00,550
♪I will rise upon those ashes♪
